{
  "texts": [
    "Q3 minus Q1 gives the IQR.",
    "Outliers are data points that fall outside the Q1 1.5 IQR or the Q3 + 1.5 IQR.",
    "A random under-sampling algorithm ensures that the data is more evenly distributed and does not cause bias.",
    "The O'Neil dataset has an unbalanced class distribution.",
    "The random under-sampling algorithm can be applied to the dataset to overcome this."
  ]
}